{"id":145,"parent_id":121,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":145,"title":"Numbers 24","subtitle":"","short_title":"Num.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/24","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 24"],[".studySummary",["i","Balaam sees in vision and prophesies of the destiny of Israel—He prophesies of the Messiah: There will come a Star out of Jacob, and a Sceptre will rise out of Israel."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/24.1","order":"02.05.024.13090"},["b","1"],"And when Balaam saw that it",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"pleased"],"the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"to bless Israel, he went not, as at other times, to seek for enchantments, but he set his face toward the wilderness."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/24.2","order":"02.05.024.13091"},["b","2"],"And Balaam lifted up his eyes, and he saw Israel abiding",["i","in his tents"],"according to their",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"tribes"],"; and the spirit of God came upon him."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/24.3","order":"02.05.024.13092"},["b","3"],"And he took up his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"parable"],", and said, Balaam the son of Beor hath said, and the man whose eyes are open hath said:"],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/24.4","order":"02.05.024.13093"},["b","4"],"He hath said, which heard the words of God, which saw the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"vision"],"of the Almighty, falling",["i","into a trance,"],"but having his eyes open:"],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/24.5","order":"02.05.024.13094"},["b","5"],"How goodly are thy tents, O Jacob,",["i","and"],"thy",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"tabernacles"],", O Israel!"],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/24.6","order":"02.05.024.13095"},["b","6"],"As the valleys are they spread forth, as gardens by the river’s side, as the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"trees"],"of lign aloes which the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"hath planted,",["i","and"],"as cedar trees beside the waters."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/24.7","order":"02.05.024.13096"},["b","7"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"He"],"shall pour the water out of his buckets, and his seed",["i","shall be"],"in many waters, and his king shall be higher than",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"Agag"],", and his kingdom shall be exalted."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/24.8","order":"02.05.024.13097"},["b","8"],"God brought him forth out of Egypt; he hath as it were the strength of an unicorn: he shall eat up the nations his enemies, and shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"break"],"their bones, and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"pierce"],["i","them"],"through with his arrows."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/24.9","order":"02.05.024.13098"},["b","9"],"He couched, he lay down as a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"lion"],", and as a great lion: who shall stir him up? Blessed",["i","is"],"he that blesseth thee, and cursed",["i","is"],"he that curseth thee."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/24.10","order":"02.05.024.13099"},["b","10"],"¶And Balak’s anger was kindled against Balaam, and he smote his hands together: and Balak said unto Balaam, I called thee to curse mine enemies, and, behold, thou hast altogether blessed",["i","them"],"these three times."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/24.11","order":"02.05.024.13100"},["b","11"],"Therefore now flee thou to thy place: I thought to promote thee unto great honour; but, lo, the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"hath kept thee back from honour."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/24.12","order":"02.05.024.13101"},["b","12"],"And Balaam said unto Balak, Spake I not also to thy messengers which thou sentest unto me, saying,"],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/24.13","order":"02.05.024.13102"},["b","13"],"If Balak would give me his house full of silver and gold, I cannot go beyond the commandment of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", to do",["i","either"],"good or bad of mine own",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"mind"],";",["i","but"],"what the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"saith, that will I",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"speak"],"?"],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/24.14","order":"02.05.024.13103"},["b","14"],"And now, behold, I go unto my people: come",["i","therefore, and"],"I will",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"advertise"],"thee what this people shall do to thy people in the latter days."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/24.15","order":"02.05.024.13104"},["b","15"],"¶And he took up his parable, and said, Balaam the son of Beor hath said, and the man whose eyes are open hath said:"],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/24.16","order":"02.05.024.13105"},["b","16"],"He hath said, which heard the words of God, and knew the knowledge of the most High,",["i","which"],"saw the vision of the Almighty, falling",["i","into a trance,"],"but having his eyes open:"],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/24.17","order":"02.05.024.13106"},["b","17"],"I shall see him, but",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"not now"],": I shall behold him, but not nigh: there shall come a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_17b"},"Star"],"out of Jacob, and a Sceptre shall rise out of Israel, and shall smite the corners of",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_17c"},"Moab"],", and destroy all the children of Sheth."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/24.18","order":"02.05.024.13107"},["b","18"],"And",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"Edom"],"shall be a possession, Seir also shall be a possession for his enemies; and Israel shall do valiantly."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/24.19","order":"02.05.024.13108"},["b","19"],"Out of Jacob shall come he that shall have dominion, and shall destroy him that remaineth of the city."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/24.20","order":"02.05.024.13109"},["b","20"],"¶And when he looked on Amalek, he took up his parable, and said,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"Amalek"],["i","was"],"the first of the nations; but his latter end",["i","shall be"],"that he perish for ever."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/24.21","order":"02.05.024.13110"},["b","21"],"And he looked on the Kenites, and took up his parable, and said, Strong is thy dwellingplace, and thou puttest thy nest in a rock."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/24.22","order":"02.05.024.13111"},["b","22"],"Nevertheless the Kenite shall be wasted, until Asshur shall carry thee away captive."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/24.23","order":"02.05.024.13112"},["b","23"],"And he took up his parable, and said, Alas, who shall live when God doeth this!"],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/24.24","order":"02.05.024.13113"},["b","24"],"And ships",["i","shall come"],"from the coast of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"Chittim"],", and shall afflict Asshur, and shall afflict Eber, and he also shall perish for ever."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/24.25","order":"02.05.024.13114"},["b","25"],"And Balaam rose up, and went and returned to his place: and Balak also went his way."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/24.1a","order":"02.05.024.13115"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/41.1"},"D&C 41:1"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/76.5"},"76:5"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/24.2a","order":"02.05.024.13117"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/num/2.2.2-31"},"Num. 2:2 (2–31)"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/24.3a","order":"02.05.024.13119"},["b","3a"],["span.small","IE"],"figurative discourse."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/24.4a","order":"02.05.024.13121"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/vision"},"TG Vision"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/24.5a","order":"02.05.024.13123"},["b","5a"],["span.small","OR"],"dwellings."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/24.6a","order":"02.05.024.13125"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/104.16.16-17"},"Ps. 104:16 (16–17)"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/24.7a","order":"02.05.024.13127"},["b","7a"],["span.small","HEB"],"Water shall flow from his branches."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/24.7b","order":"02.05.024.13129"},["b","7b"],["span.small","IE"],"the Amalekites."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/24.8a","order":"02.05.024.13131"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/50.17"},"Jer. 50:17"],"."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/24.8b","order":"02.05.024.13133"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/50.9"},"Jer. 50:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/24.9a","order":"02.05.024.13135"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/49.9"},"Gen. 49:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/24.13a","order":"02.05.024.13137"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/mind"},"TG Mind"],"."],["div",{"id":"13b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/24.13b","order":"02.05.024.13139"},["b","13b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/2.7.6-8"},"Ezek. 2:7 (6–8)"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/24.14a","order":"02.05.024.13141"},["b","14a"],["span.small","HEB"],"tell."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/24.17a","order":"02.05.024.13143"},["b","17a"],["span.small","IE"],"His coming was to be in the future, long after Moses’ time."],["div",{"id":"17b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/24.17b","order":"02.05.024.13145"},["b","17b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-prophecies-about"},"TG Jesus Christ, Prophecies about"],"."],["div",{"id":"17c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/24.17c","order":"02.05.024.13147"},["b","17c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/8.2"},"2 Sam. 8:2"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.45"},"Jer. 48:45"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/24.18a","order":"02.05.024.13149"},["b","18a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/8.14"},"2 Sam. 8:14"],"."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/24.20a","order":"02.05.024.13151"},["b","20a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/17.8.8-16"},"Ex. 17:8 (8–16)"],"."],["div",{"id":"24a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/24.24a","order":"02.05.024.13153"},["b","24a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/dan/11.30"},"Dan. 11:30"],"."]]}
